KISS Wayland Repository
________________________________________________________________________________

A KISS Linux repository for Wayland packages.

After the archival of sdsddsd1's mywayland[1] repo I needed a way to continue
getting updates to my wayland install, and thus kiss-wayland was born.

If a package you used/want is missing, feel free to make a pr adding it the
repo, so far I've only got the ones I use added.

To use this repo you should have the following repositories in your KISS_PATH:
 - kisslinux/repo/*    [2]
 - kisslinux/community [3]


Mirrors
________________________________________________________________________________

This git repository is mirrored to the following locations:

 - https://git.himmalerin.net/kiss-wayland
 - https://github.com/Himmalerin/kiss-wayland
 - https://git.sr.ht/~himmalerin/kiss-wayland


